ico_data.description: MyBit makes financing and maintaining revenue streams efficient and automatic for the renewable energy sector. MyBit does this by commoditizing solar panel and other renewable energy installation. Investors can invest in renewable energy while landowners can find the capital needed to build a decentralized energy grid.
